Author: Blacknbruisey
Text: Remember: you don't know those people. They are only posting their positive results and not what goes on behind the scenes. Many of them could very well be struggling with an ED too; they just arent posting about it. Dont believe everything you see on the internet. People hide and lie all the time. Though they may appear "normal", they're only leading us to believe that.   Don't be ashamed and you are never a failure.

Author: bruno_guy
Text: i feel the same way. i did  intermittent fasting and i didnt even see any results, and i blamed myself that i didn't work hard enough or  restrict hard enough and that's why i didn't get any results. i also feel ashamed that i can't eat like a normal person even though i want to so bad, i just really wish i can go back 6 months ago and redo my life and thoughts on weight loss and a good eating habits.
